data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bed, 2 bath home in Cleburne,TX! Starting with the heart of the home, the eat-in kitchen, opens up to the fabulously spacious living room. Imagine the countless hours you'll spend in this space, creating culinary masterpieces, enjoying quality time with family and friends. You’ll find a lovely fireplace in the living room to cozy up to with a warm cup of cocoa on chilly evenings, creating lifetime memories. The bedrooms are adorned with plush carpets, with tile throughout the house. Get ready to entertain in style with the large backyard with a extended patio with pergola where you can truly soak in the beauty.  Perfect for enjoying the delightful vibrant Texas skies. Another amazing feature that will have you falling head over heels in love with this home. Prepare to be pampered in your new jacuzzi after a long day! An absolute dream home come true, with its impeccable features and inviting ambiance. Don't miss this home!
